OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Len Trewin
OL,5,FLen Trewin, Age 100, Parachute Regiment
OL,7,FInterviewed 25 July 2024
OL,9,FVolunteering for the Parachute
OL,10,FRegiment and joining the 8th
OL,11,FBattalion, Mr Trewin spent months
OL,12,Ftraining before being deployed to
OL,13,FNormandy in the weeks following the
OL,14,Finvasion. He flew over the English
OL,15,FChannel in a Dakota from an air base
OL,16,Fin Gloucestershire
OL,18,F"It was about falling and rolling to
OL,19,Ftake the shock of the drop," he said.
