OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Len Trewin
OL,5,F"We took off. Didn't know, a mystery.
OL,6,FWe just dropped wondering what was
OL,7,Fgoing to happen. It's three seconds
OL,8,Ffrom when you leave the plane to when
OL,9,Fyou hit the ground.
OL,11,F"You haven't got time to think.
OL,13,F"You've got too much to do.
OL,15,F"The job, with a rifle strapped to
OL,16,Fyour leg. You have to lower that and
OL,17,Fthen you have to orient your position
OL,18,Fwhere you're going to land. Everything
OL,19,Ffalls into place. When you jump it's
OL,20,Fthe biggest shambles ever but you soon
OL,21,Fsort yourself out.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
