OL,5,F"What we used was coloured smoke for
OL,6,Fdifferent companies and different
OL,7,Fbattalions."
OL,9,FMr Trewin took part in the battle for
OL,10,FCaen - a key strategic target for the
OL,11,FAllies. It took them until the first
OL,12,Fweek of August to take control of the
OL,13,Fcity and vicinity.
OL,15,FHe said: "You automatically become
OL,16,Finvolved in the fighting and then you
OL,17,Fhave patrols to do and different
OL,18,Fthings. You shut your mind to it. You
OL,19,Fhave to.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
